Package hr.fer.zemris.java.hw04.custom.collections

Class Dictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.hw04.custom.collections.Dictionary

  • public class Dictionary
extends java.lang.Object
    The class represents a simple map that memorises a single value connected to a unique key. Keys must not be null, but values can.
    Author:
    Dorian Ivankovic
